{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_05_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 力を貸してほしい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（よし、スケジュールの調整はバッチリだな）\n（けどこれは、年末のライブに向けて忙しくなるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Alright‚ the schedule is perfectly adjusted.)\n(But this is going to get busy for the year-end live.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7807195028,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5285.947163899999,
          "startTime": 10.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、ちょうど良かった\n今日のスケジュールについてなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ it's good that I caught you.\nI wanted to talk to you about today's schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ここ数日、レッスンばかりだよね？\n何か他に仕事って入ってないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been focused on lessons these past few days‚ right?\nIs there anything else scheduled besides that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、特に今のところは何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ not really‚ nothing at the moment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……いや、それならそれでいいんだ\nじゃ、レッスンに行ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Well‚ if that's the case‚ it's fine.\nI'll be heading to my lesson then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6666672398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ alright…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666667000015,
          "startTime": 34.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さすが年末だ。忙し過ぎて体が足りないな）\n（ 事務作業をさばいたら、レッスンの付き添いに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As expected‚ it's getting hectic towards the year-end.)\n(After handling office work‚ it's time for lesson support…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.9999999999986,
          "startTime": 47.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "君はなんだか、いつもバタバタしているね\n僕達よりもやることが多そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You always seem so busy.\nIt looks like you have more to do than us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、葵？　どうして……\n今日はボーカルレッスンだったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Aoi? Why are you…\nToday was supposed to be vocal lessons‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだけど、もっと他に大事な用事があってね\nこっそり抜け出してきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was‚ but I have something more important to do.\nI snuck away for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、その用事っていうのは\n君に関することだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ that important matter I mentioned…\nIt's related to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺？　そうか……ただ、ごめん\n見ての通り手が回ってなくて。改めて時間を作って――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me? I see… I'm sorry.\nAs you can see‚ I'm swamped. I'll make time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "忙しさを理由に逃げないでよ\n僕は今、真剣な話がしたくてここにいるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't use busyness as an excuse.\nI'm here because I want to have a serious talk with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、君が忙しくしているのは全部\n星見プロのアイドル達のためだって知ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that you're working hard\nfor all the idols at Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "とてもありがたいことだって理解もしている\nけど……正直最近、レッスンばかりでもどかしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I truly appreciate it.\nBut… honestly‚ lately‚ it's frustrating that it's all just lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5745722784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "もどかしい……\nグループ内で、何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Frustrating…\nDid something happen within the group?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "いや。むしろ、何もないんだよ\n何も変化がない。それがもどかしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's the opposite. Nothing is happening.\nThere's been no change. It's frustrating.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "I-UNITY以降、愛もこころも、うんと成長した\n今が一番リズノワとして整ってると言っていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I-UNITY‚ both Ai and Kokoro have improved significantly.\nRight now‚ they're at their best as LizNoir members.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "でも逆に、頭打ちだ。変化が足りないんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at the same time‚ it feels like we've hit a plateau.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして葵は、焦っているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you feeling impatient‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "……どうだろう。分からない\nでも、そうなのかもしれないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I don't know. I'm not sure.\nBut maybe… I am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロにスリクスまで加入したし\n知名度でも他のグループに水をあけられてる気がするし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even IIIX has joined Hoshimi Prods.‚\nit feels like we're being overshadowed in terms of popularity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……めずらしいな\n葵がそういうことを気にするなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's unusual.\nAoi‚ you've never seemed to care about such things.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "そうだね。自分でも驚いてるよ\n前はこんなこと、気にならなかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. I'm surprised at myself too.\nI never used to think about this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "自分が自分じゃないみたいで、時々気持ち悪いよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like I'm not myself sometimes‚ and it's unsettling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん、ネガティブに捉えないでくれ\nむしろこれは、いい傾向だと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't view this negatively.\nI actually think it's a good sign.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "いい傾向？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A good sign?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "葵のそれは、向上心からくる結果への焦りだろう\n成長する上で最大級の原動力になる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ what you're feeling is the impatience that comes from your ambition to excel.\nIt's the most powerful driving force for improvement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "そういうものなの？\nモヤモヤしてレッスンの邪魔にしかなってないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so?\nEven though this impatience is just making me frustrated during lessons…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "モヤモヤさせてしまってるのは、俺のカバー不足だよ\nすまない。もっとみんなとしっかり話すべきだったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you're feeling frustrated‚ it's because I haven't provided enough support.\nI'm sorry. I should have talked more with everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.2098989632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "それは本当にそう。気付いてくれて何よりだよ\n僕が大事な用事だって言ってた意味、理解した？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true. I appreciate you realizing it.\nDo you understand the reason I said this was an important matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、した\nそれで具体的に、葵は俺にどうしてほしいんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I do.\nSo‚ specifically‚ what would you like me to do‚ Aoi?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "僕にもっと、仕事を取ってきてほしい\nライブや歌番組以外でも、なんでもいいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want you to secure more work for us.\nNot just live shows and music programs‚ anything is fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 219.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "けど葵は、そういう仕事を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Aoi‚ you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "うん。正直、必要ないと思ってたよ\nリズノワはパフォーマンスで勝負するグループだからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. Honestly‚ I used to think that.\nLizNoir competes with our performances‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "でも、悔しいけど……\nそれだけじゃダメなのかもって、限界を感じてるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's frustrating…\nIt might not be enough to aim for the top just with performances.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 238.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "これまで以上にリズノワが勝ち上がって\n頂点を狙っていくには、それだけじゃきっと足りない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That alone is probably not enough for LizNoir\nto win more than ever and aim for the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "僕自身も変わる必要があると思うんだ\n今まで避けてきた仕事にも挑戦する……とかさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I need to change too.\nI need to challenge jobs I've avoided until now… and such.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}君\n僕達をもっと、売り込んでほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}…\nI want you to promote us more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "葵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "僕達リズノワは、もっと上を目指せるはずなんだ\nこんな所で頭打ちになってる場合じゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir has the potential to aim higher.\nWe can't afford to plateau like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリで月ストに、I-UNITYでトリエルに負けて\n旬が終わったなんて思われたくない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want people to think that my season is over after I lost\nto Moon Tempest at the Grand Prix and Toriel at I-UNITY.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.4058804136,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "何より僕は――\n莉央を勝たせたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Above all‚\nI want to help Rio win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.6000079836,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi029.m4a",
      "text": "そのためなら\n僕はどんな仕事だってする覚悟は出来てるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it means doing any kind of job‚\nI'm prepared for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi030.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君……力を貸してほしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}… I hope you can help us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……何言ってるんだ、葵\n――頼まれるまでもなく、最初からそのつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What are you saying‚ Aoi?\nI've been planning to do that from the beginning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi031.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 302.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "必ず「これだ！」っていう、いい仕事を取ってくるよ\nだから、もう少しだけ待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll definitely find us some great opportunities.\nSo‚ please wait a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi032.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった。頼りにしてるよ\nありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Understood. I'm counting on you.\nThank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}